### Entity

#### BaseEntity
```java
@MappedSuperclass
@Data
@NoArgsConstructor
@AllArgsConstructor
public class BaseEntity implements Serializable {
    @Id
    // 如果strategy采用GenerationType.IDENTITY，使用数据库的自增主键，不会生成sequence表
    @GeneratedValue
    private Long id;

    @Column(updatable = false)
    @CreationTimestamp
    private Date createTime;

    @UpdateTimestamp
    private Date updateTime;
}
```

